<PageTitle>About</PageTitle>

<h1>About AbeGaming</h1>

<p>
    AbeGaming is a hobby project created to explore modern web development with Blazor WebAssembly 
    while building useful tools for board gaming enthusiasts.
</p>

<p>
    The app is designed as a Progressive Web App (PWA), meaning you can <a href="home">install</a> it on your device
    and use it offline - perfect for game nights where internet access might be limited.
</p>

<h2>Current Features</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>For The People Battle Calculator</strong> - A tool to resolve land battles in the award-winning 
    American Civil War card-driven strategy game "For The People" by GMT Games.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Technology</h2>
<p>
    This application is built with:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Blazor WebAssembly (.NET 10)</li>
    <li>Hosted on Cloudflare Pages</li>
    <li>PWA-enabled for offline support</li>
</ul>

